<br>
I've played a lot with 2 mage + 1 cleric groups &amp; i've never, ever seen a mob hit a pet when a pc has been available to be whacked on (and was on the hate list - i.e. a pet engaged with a mob will never attack the cleric even if the cleric stands in meele range &amp; chs the pet over &amp; over...but if the cleric heals/buffs one of the mages, then the mob will prefer the cleric 100% of the time over both mage pets).<br>
<br>
I have, however, seen necro pets take agro with a pc in range, but never a mage pet /shrug <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=412980">Lorcann</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
