We did Team Magi trials a week or so ago.  We had fun, learned a lot, and didn't win.  =)  I have neglected to post a full writeup but here are a few things we learned.<br>
<br>
1]  PrePoP pets just don't cut it.  They die too fast, and don't do enough DPS.<br>
<br>
2]  It is hard to assist on the MA while they are chain casting pets.  =P<br>
<br>
3]  2 people died once.  All other Team Magi tries (4 to 5 I think) we had no deaths.<br>
<br>
4]  3 Members have PoP pets, and we will be back.  =)<br>
